&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7795&quot; title=&quot;least_qunit should be tunnable&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7795&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7795&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; quota: tuneable soft least qunit&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6433&quot; title=&quot;MDS deadlock in qouta  &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6433&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6433&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; quota: handle QUOTA_DQACQ in READPAGE portal&lt;br/&gt;
